summary_topics
  trigger "summarize|summarise|summary of|one-paragraph summary|резюме|кратко изоб|कृपया सारांश|सारांश|概括|总结"
  reject_substring "conversation|chat|беседы|чата|बातचीत|聊天|对话"
  reject_exact summarize
  constraint_marker "one paragraph"
  constraint_marker one-paragraph
  constraint_label one_paragraph
  fallback_body "<topic> summary: the request is recorded as a bounded summarization task with a topic, constraint, and trace link."
  topic Rust
    detection_keywords "rust|раст|러스트|रस्ट|锈语言"
    body "Rust is a systems programming language focused on performance, memory safety, and concurrency. It prevents many memory errors at compile time through ownership and borrowing, while still compiling to native machine code."
  topic Wikipedia
    detection_keywords "wikipedia|википедии|википедия|википедию|विकिपीडिया|维基百科"
    body "Wikipedia is a free multilingual encyclopedia maintained by volunteer contributors. Its articles are collaboratively edited, cite external sources, and are connected to structured Wikimedia projects such as Wikidata."
  topic formal-ai
    detection_keywords "formal-ai|formal ai|формал-ай|formalाई|福尔玛尔-人工智能"
    body "formal-ai is a deterministic symbolic assistant that routes prompts through Links Notation-backed rules, records reasoning events, and exposes OpenAI-shaped API surfaces without neural-network inference."
